comments: Bazemore (POR) cleanly pokes the ball away from Graham (CHA).

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Bazemore (POR) throws the ball out of bounds.
Bazemore (POR) makes contact with Graham's (CHA) wrist on the perimeter that affects his SQBR.
Zeller (CHA) makes marginal contact with Bazemore (POR) as he disengages from the contact.
Anthony (POR) makes marginal contact with Zeller's (CHA) non-shooting arm during the play at the basket.
McCollum (POR) makes marginal contact with Rozier (CHA) as he disengages from the contact at the end of the drive.
Zeller (CHA) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Bazemore (POR) makes foot to foot contact and does not give Rozier (CHA) room to land on the jump shot attempt.
There is no conclusive angle showing whether Anthony (POR) steps out of bounds as he intercepts the pass.
Graham (CHA) commits a take foul on Tolliver (POR).
Anthony (POR) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Batum (CHA) makes marginal contact with Lillard (POR) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt. Williams (CHA) maintains a legal vertical position.
Zeller (CHA) sets the screen in Bazemore's (POR) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Batum (CHA) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
Anthony (POR) clamps Washington's (CHA) arm and affects his ability to get to the rebound.
Graham (CHA) extends his arm into Lillard's (POR) back and dislodges him while pursuing the long rebound.
McCollum (POR) grasps Rozier's (CHA) arm affecting his FOM.
Bazemore (POR) legally contests Graham's (CHA) jump shot attempt.
